original: There was once a chubby cat that enjoyed spinning in circles. However, one day, the cat slipped on a slick floor and injured its leg, rendering it unable to spin any longer. This left the cat feeling very disheartened. The end.
sampled: There was once a chubby feline that enjoyed revolving in circles. However, one day, the cat slipped on a slick floor and injured its leg, rendering it unable to spin any longer. This left the cat feeling very disheartened. The end.
